        "content": "# ü§ñ AI Telegram Bot Workflow\n\n**Overview:**\nThis workflow creates an intelligent Telegram bot that:\n- Remembers conversation history\n- Responds to commands (/start, /clear)\n- Uses NVIDIA's mistralai/mistral-nemotron model for AI responses\n- Handles different message types appropriately\n\n**Required Credentials:**\n- Telegram Bot API token\n- NVIDIA API Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE"
