        "content": "## üîÄ Message Routing Logic\n\n**Step 1:** All incoming messages are processed through multiple IF nodes to determine the appropriate response:\n\n1. **Start Command** ‚Üí Welcome message\n2. **Clear Command** ‚Üí Clear chat history\n3. **Regular Text** ‚Üí AI processing\n4. **Non-text Messages** ‚Üí Error message\n\nThis ensures each message type gets handled correctly."
